{"title":"关于姥姥的采访","authors":["赵凌"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":3,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于姥姥的采访"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵凌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞外公偷偷告诉我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姥姥年轻时候不美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梳最简单的短发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿最朴素的蓝裙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她没有时间爱自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为爱的孩子太多"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姥姥退休了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过老花镜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把各种颜色的花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绣满床罩、椅垫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电视机套和我的裙子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她一翻开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去的相册"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看着看着就流泪说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不和你们一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿件花衣服"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和学生合影呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张新耘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸上已经布满皱纹时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才感觉自己笑得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好看些了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗯，这不是做作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那个时候起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就已经努力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把秋天和冬天一齐打进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望的包裹里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贴上邮票"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夜深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无人的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄到四季是春的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}